    "No writes in the last minute — Pulse may have lost a permission. Open Settings → Diagnostics or recheck Input Monitoring + Accessibility under System Settings.": {
      "comment": "DiagnosticsCard silent-failure warning. Reworded in A30 to give the user a concrete next step (where to look) instead of just naming the failure mode.",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "No writes in the last minute — Pulse may have lost a permission. Open Settings → Diagnostics or recheck Input Monitoring + Accessibility under System Settings."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "过去一分钟没有新数据 —— Pulse 可能丢失了权限。打开「设置 → 诊断」，或在系统设置里重新确认「输入监控」和「辅助功能」。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
