    "No system events in the past hour. This table fills in when your Mac sleeps, wakes, locks, opens or closes the lid, or flips a Focus mode.": {
      "comment": "Privacy audit — empty-state placeholder for the system events table. Explains both what a system event *is* and why the window can be legitimately empty.",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "No system events in the past hour. This table fills in when your Mac sleeps, wakes, locks, opens or closes the lid, or flips a Focus mode."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "过去一小时没有系统事件。当你的 Mac 进入或唤醒睡眠、锁定、合盖或开盖、切换专注模式时，这张表才会有内容。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Pulse runs entirely on your Mac. The only outbound traffic is the GitHub Releases check that runs *only* when you click \"Check for updates…\" — never on a schedule, never in the background.": {
      "comment": "Privacy audit footer — accurately describes the network behaviour of the shipping app: Sparkle update check is the only outbound call, and it's user-initiated.",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Pulse runs entirely on your Mac. The only outbound traffic is the GitHub Releases check that runs *only* when you click \"Check for updates…\" — never on a schedule, never in the background."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Pulse 完全运行在你的 Mac 本地。唯一的对外网络流量是「检查更新…」按钮触发的 GitHub Releases 查询 —— 仅在你主动点击时执行，绝不会按计划运行，也绝不会在后台静默触发。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Reading the database…": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Reading the database…"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "正在读取数据库…"
          }
        }
      }
    },
