            "state": "translated",
            "value": "第 %lld 步，共 %lld 步"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Short-form work — lots of 5-to-15-minute sessions today.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Short-form work — lots of 5-to-15-minute sessions today."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "短节奏工作——今天有不少 5 到 15 分钟的会话。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Checker mode — mostly quick dips today, not long-form focus.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Checker mode — mostly quick dips today, not long-form focus."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "检查员模式——今天基本是短停留，不是长段深度专注。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Welcome to Pulse": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Welcome to Pulse"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "欢迎使用 Pulse"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "A local-first dashboard for the way you actually use your Mac. Pulse turns the noisy stream of clicks, key presses, scrolls and app switches into a daily story you can read in 30 seconds.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "A local-first dashboard for the way you actually use your Mac. Pulse turns the noisy stream of clicks, key presses, scrolls and app switches into a daily story you can read in 30 seconds."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "本地优先的仪表盘，记录你真正使用 Mac 的方式。Pulse 把点击、按键、滚动、应用切换这些嘈杂的事件流，整理成 30 秒就能读完的每日故事。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Privacy promises": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Privacy promises"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "隐私承诺"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Before we ask for any permissions, here is what Pulse will and will not do — read it first.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Before we ask for any permissions, here is what Pulse will and will not do — read it first."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "在请求任何权限之前，先把 Pulse 会做和不会做的事讲清楚——请先读完。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "All raw data stays in Pulse's private folder on your Mac. Nothing is ever uploaded.": {
      "comment": "Onboarding privacy pledge — storage location bullet. De-jargoned from the previous '~/Library/Application Support/Pulse/' filesystem path so users without macOS-internals knowledge can still parse the promise.",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "All raw data stays in Pulse's private folder on your Mac. Nothing is ever uploaded."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "所有原始数据都保留在 Pulse 的本地私有文件夹里，永远不会上传。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "No keystroke contents — only press counts. By default the key code itself isn't stored either.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "No keystroke contents — only press counts. By default the key code itself isn't stored either."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "不记录按键内容 —— 只记录按键次数。默认连键码本身也不存。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "No clipboard content, no screen recording, no microphone, no camera, ever. (Pulse only reads the pasteboard's incrementing change counter to count copy/cut frequency — never the text or files on it.)": {
      "comment": "Onboarding privacy pledge. Updated 2026-05 for F-32 accuracy: Pulse reads NSPasteboard.changeCount but not the pasteboard contents — the original pledge said 'no clipboard' which was technically loose.",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "No clipboard content, no screen recording, no microphone, no camera, ever. (Pulse only reads the pasteboard's incrementing change counter to count copy/cut frequency — never the text or files on it.)"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "永远不读剪贴板内容、不录屏、不开麦克风、不开摄像头。（Pulse 只读取系统剪贴板每次变动的递增计数，用来统计复制/剪切频率 —— 不读上面的任何文字或文件。）"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Window titles are hashed before they're written to disk, so Pulse can count app switches without storing what was on the screen.": {
      "comment": "Onboarding privacy pledge — window-title hashing bullet. Reworded to explain *why* hashing is in the pipeline; the previous 'SHA-256 hashed' phrasing was technically precise but offered no narrative for users unfamiliar with the term.",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Window titles are hashed before they're written to disk, so Pulse can count app switches without storing what was on the screen."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "窗口标题在写入磁盘前会先经过哈希，让 Pulse 可以统计 App 切换次数，但不会存下你屏幕上显示的内容。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Update checks only run when you click “Check for updates…”. Pulse fetches a Sparkle appcast from GitHub Releases at that moment and never on a schedule.": {
      "comment": "Onboarding privacy pledge. Updated 2026-05: Sparkle update checker is shipped — text now reflects the actual user-initiated trigger instead of saying it's a 'future' feature.",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Update checks only run when you click “Check for updates…”. Pulse fetches a Sparkle appcast from GitHub Releases at that moment and never on a schedule."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "只有你点击「检查更新…」时 Pulse 才会发起一次出站请求 —— 在那一刻从 GitHub Releases 拉取 Sparkle appcast，绝不在后台按计划自动检查。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "I've read these promises and want to continue.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "I've read these promises and want to continue."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "我已经读过这些承诺，希望继续。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Grant Input Monitoring": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Grant Input Monitoring"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "授权 Input Monitoring"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Grant Accessibility": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Grant Accessibility"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "授权 Accessibility"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Grant permission": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Grant permission"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "授权"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Pulse uses Input Monitoring to count clicks, key presses and scroll ticks system-wide. **It only counts events — it never records what you type.** macOS will quit and relaunch Pulse the moment you flip the switch; that's normal.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Pulse uses Input Monitoring to count clicks, key presses and scroll ticks system-wide. **It only counts events — it never records what you type.** macOS will quit and relaunch Pulse the moment you flip the switch; that's normal."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Pulse 使用 Input Monitoring 在系统层面统计点击、按键、滚动次数。**只数事件本身，绝不记录你打了什么。** 你勾选这个开关时 macOS 会立即退出并重启 Pulse，这是正常现象。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Pulse uses Accessibility to read which app is in the foreground and (optionally) the title of the active window. Window titles are hashed before being stored.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Pulse uses Accessibility to read which app is in the foreground and (optionally) the title of the active window. Window titles are hashed before being stored."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Pulse 使用 Accessibility 来识别当前前台应用，以及（可选地）当前活跃窗口的标题。窗口标题会先被哈希再落盘。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "This permission is required for Pulse to function.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "This permission is required for Pulse to function."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Pulse 需要这个权限才能正常工作。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Click **Open System Settings** below.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Click **Open System Settings** below."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "点下方的 **打开系统设置**。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Find **Pulse** in the list.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Find **Pulse** in the list."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "在列表中找到 **Pulse**。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Toggle the switch on. macOS may ask for your password.": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Toggle the switch on. macOS may ask for your password."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "把开关打开。macOS 可能会让你输入密码。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "macOS will close Pulse so the new permission takes effect — that's expected. Just reopen Pulse from your Applications folder; this onboarding will pick up right where it left off.": {
      "comment": "Onboarding Input Monitoring step 4 — reassures the user that Pulse being force-quit is normal, not a crash, and tells them how to resume.",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "macOS will close Pulse so the new permission takes effect — that's expected. Just reopen Pulse from your Applications folder; this onboarding will pick up right where it left off."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "macOS 会关闭 Pulse 以让新权限生效 —— 这是预期行为，不是崩溃。从「应用程序」文件夹里重新打开 Pulse 即可，引导流程会接着上次的位置继续。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Open System Settings": {
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Open System Settings"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "打开系统设置"
          }
        }
      }
    },
