            "state": "translated",
            "value": "You're set"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "准备好了"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Pulse is now collecting your activity locally. Open the menu bar icon any time to pause, peek at today's numbers, or browse what Pulse has recorded. Come back tomorrow morning — the first time you wake your Mac you'll see a one-page briefing of yesterday's run.": {
      "comment": "Onboarding final-step copy — celebrates the setup and tells the user what to expect tomorrow (the first daily briefing).",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Pulse is now collecting your activity locally. Open the menu bar icon any time to pause, peek at today's numbers, or browse what Pulse has recorded. Come back tomorrow morning — the first time you wake your Mac you'll see a one-page briefing of yesterday's run."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Pulse 已经开始在本地采集你的活动了。任何时候点击菜单栏图标都能暂停、查看今日数据，或浏览 Pulse 记录了什么。明早再来 —— 你下一次唤醒 Mac 时，会看到一页关于昨天的简报。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Based on US-QWERTY key positions — bars may not reflect physical hands on Dvorak or Colemak.": {
      "comment": "F-20 HandBalanceCard footnote — disclaims the static QWERTY-keyed left/right classification so users on alternate layouts know why the bars may not match their physical hands.",
      "localizations": {
        "en": { "stringUnit": { "state": "translated", "value": "Based on US-QWERTY key positions — bars may not reflect physical hands on Dvorak or Colemak." } },
        "zh-Hans": { "stringUnit": { "state": "translated", "value": "基于 US-QWERTY 键位划分 —— 在 Dvorak / Colemak 等其他键盘布局上，左右比例可能与你实际的左右手不符。" } }
      }
    },
