    "Sets which feed “Check for updates…” queries. Flip the toggle, then click the button below — Pulse will install the most recent build of the channel you just switched to.": {
      "comment": "Settings About — caption under the dev builds toggle. Toggle = preference + primer; the existing Check for updates… button is the action. No separate cross-channel button — flipping the toggle arms a one-shot version-compare override so the next check installs the new channel's latest build.",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Sets which feed “Check for updates…” queries. Flip the toggle, then click the button below — Pulse will install the most recent build of the channel you just switched to."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "决定「检查更新…」从哪条 feed 拉取。翻动这个开关之后，再点下面的「检查更新…」按钮 —— Pulse 会装上你刚切到的频道的最新构建。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Version": {
      "comment": "Settings About — label for the row showing the running version + build number.",
