        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Pulse 上次异常退出"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "macOS saved a crash log when this happened. Open it if you want to see what went wrong (or share it for debugging), or dismiss this banner — it won't reappear unless another crash happens.": {
      "comment": "F-49b CrashBeaconBanner — body text explaining the crash report and dismiss behavior. Reworded in A31 to drop 'stack trace' jargon and frame the action as 'see what went wrong / share for debugging' instead.",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "macOS saved a crash log when this happened. Open it if you want to see what went wrong (or share it for debugging), or dismiss this banner — it won't reappear unless another crash happens."
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "上次崩溃时 macOS 保存了一份崩溃日志。你可以打开它看看出了什么问题（或把它分享出去用于排错），也可以忽略这条提示 —— 只有下次再崩溃时它才会重新出现。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
